132
00:11:59,537 --> 00:12:03,584
<i>Ak príde koniec sveta zapamätaj si...</i>

133
00:12:03,662 --> 00:12:05,162
Prepáč.

134
00:12:05,912 --> 00:12:12,348
<i>...že sa moja láska k tebe nikdy nezmení</i>

135
00:12:12,373 --> 00:12:17,498
