195
00:17:25,341 --> 00:17:27,927
- ale...
- To Tharn ju kúpil!

196
00:17:30,013 --> 00:17:31,670
A vôbec sa za to nehanbí.

197
00:17:31,695 --> 00:17:34,239
Nemám problém investovať do takej veci.

198
00:17:35,253 --> 00:17:37,153
Už pôjdeme.

199
00:17:38,466 --> 00:17:39,667
Majte sa.

200
00:17:39,692 --> 00:17:40,764
