Poďme, chcem ťa zjesť.

205
00:17:51,713 --> 00:17:52,754
Zjesť?

206
00:17:52,779 --> 00:17:53,986
Chcem s tebou jesť.

207
00:17:54,011 --> 00:17:55,854
Oh, dobre.

208
00:17:55,879 --> 00:17:59,727
Bože, ale je zima.
Nejak ma striaslo.

209
00:18:21,957 --> 00:18:23,136
