210
00:18:23,230 --> 00:18:26,409
Oh, Tin.
Prišiel si vyzdvihnúť Can-a?

211
00:18:28,781 --> 00:18:29,862
A čo ty?

212
00:18:30,811 --> 00:18:33,316
Idem domov, Tin.

213
00:18:34,008 --> 00:18:36,324
